&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In this critical engineering leadership role, you would be responsible for building &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp; leading a high-performance R&amp;amp;D center at Pune by leveraging a robust cross-functional team of iZealiant and Razorpay leadership. Pune is being developed as the second largest strategic development center for Razorpay after Bangalore and will be home to all Banking products and services under the Razorpay umbrella. You would also be responsible to help teams define the technology and business roadmaps, enable the teams to deliver on the roadmap, and be effective in making and executing critical decisions. You would also be expected to demonstrate strong leadership in actively embedding our cultural values and enabling world-class employee engagement for this center. This leader will have direct management responsibility for product engineering teams as well as site-wide responsibilities as a central contact for all employees on the site, as we expand other functions over time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Hire the best talent, create an environment for continuous learning and growth, and enable the teams to deliver performant, resilient, highly available software at scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work effectively with the Razorpay executive team, including R&amp;amp;D, product, finance, human resources, and more to grow the Pune center. Oversee the site operations including recruitment, facilities, HR, and finance as needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Demonstrate a strong sense of ownership and integrity, proven through clear communication and collaboration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Establish best practices and bring compliance to the set execution process across org. Conceptualize and institutionalize quality and operational metrics in the organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Evangelize and role model Customer FIRST mindset with a deeper understanding of the domain, Deliver world-class solutions to business problems, Increasing agility by using the wisdom of your team to streamline how work gets done.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work and collaborate with cross functional teams, business analysts, designers, and architects to plan and execute in an agile way&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Operate with scale amid business needs and tech growth of the company. Ability to manage flux and keep things fluid as we ramp up on our journey&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Setup best practices for development and champion their adoption. Design robust and scalable solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work on a model of performance evaluation and constant feedback to make the team and himself better. Work on a model of continuous improvement for all. Participate in the full software development life cycle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;15 + years overall experience with 5+ years senior leadership experience in a fast growing company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Preferably have managed a large engineering teams in a cloud-first company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills with the ability to present complex plans and designs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Exceptional engineering leadership ability, including recruiting, inspiring, and retaining talent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deep understanding of technologies and architecture in a highly scalable and available environment. Knowledge in Cloud Technologies, CI/CD, Jenkins, and Testing methodologies is preferred&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent design and architecture knowledge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Entrepreneurial mentality, hunger, and passion to build HPOR along with strong program and product management skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Candidates must be innovative, creative, flexible, and self-motivated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Demonstrated data-driven decision making and strong customer empathy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent judgment, organizational, and problem-solving skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Educational Qualifications: Masters/Bachelors Degree in Computer Science or equivalent&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
