&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Experience in a solution management role with focus on the payments ecosystem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Experience working with payment gateways, PSPs, payment networks, merchant service providers, issuers, and acquirers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Experience on working directly with banks or merchants as the customer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Platform product management experience, building products that can be leveraged by a variety of business customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Experience in working with solutions from ideation to launch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Ability to work directly with engineers to develop use cases, build inspiring narratives, prioritize features, and evaluate short-term vs. long-term trade-offs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Ability to influence across a diverse set of stakeholders like engineers, operations, finance, compliance, legal etc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Ability to clearly articulate the story for what problem you’re solving for and the vision you’re going after, combined with the capacity to dive into minute details when necessary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Decision making skills: given limited resources, how do you prioritize across needs?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Thrive in a startup culture: dealing with fast pace, changing needs, and limited resources&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualification :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Relevant industry experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Must have exposure Program &amp;amp; Stakeholder Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Must have Functional &amp;amp; Technical expertise&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The Razorpay Cross border team has grown tremendously over the past two years and we have no intentions of slowing down. We help Indian businesses scale by selling to international customers by enabling them to collect payments from across the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You are an adept salesperson, capable of engaging in business-level and technical conversations at multiple levels of the organization, including the C-Suite as well as functional leaders. You are capable of initiating these conversations and leading the deal to a conclusion with large technology companies. You have an in-depth understanding of the buyer journey and can lead a complex, multi-party sale in a highly consultative manner, deeply understanding their strategy and how Razorpay Cross Border Portfolio can be a critical component of that. You are used to building value in competitive situations and enjoy working on products that require deep product understanding, combined with technical knowledge. Finally, you enjoy building – you like to actively participate in the development of our sales process, the articulation of our value proposition, and the creation of key tools and assets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;If you’re motivated, smart, persistent, and a great teammate, we want to hear from you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop outbound strategies to create and nurture opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Own the full sales cycle from lead to close for high-growth technology companies and Enterprise Businesses in India.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop relationships with executive stakeholders at new and existing clients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Work with company leaders from multiple functions (e.g., Engineering, Product, and Finance) to lead complex product workshops and solutioning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Lead and contribute to team projects to develop and refine our sales process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Engage with Product and Engineering teams to help drive product strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You enjoy travelling and have the ability to travel 20-30% of the time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;5-7 years of technology sales experience with a focus on field sales (quota-carrying).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Sales experience, preferably selling a technical product, with a track record of top performance for several years running.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to understand complex technical requirements and craft solutions across multiple products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to develop and execute account plans spanning multiple business units across complex organizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong presentation skills, particularly for in-person meetings with multiple stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Knowledgeable about Fintech/ Payments/ Crossborder space.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Proven ability to lead complex negotiations involving bespoke commercial agreements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ezetap by Razorpay is looking for highly motivated and skilled people experienced in managing direct enterprise sales. This role is responsible for identifying and creating new qualified opportunities within the target Enterprise segment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Increasing sales through convincing customers and partners of our capabilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Establishing, growing, and maintaining commercial ties with clients—both current and potential—in the designated territory or market segment in order to attract new clients for our goods and services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Creating a sales funnel, long-term goals, and business planning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Keeping an eye out for changes in the customer&#39;s organisation that could have an impact on future business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Coordinating sales efforts with product groups, marketing, sales management, accounting, and logistics.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Independently locating and acquiring new consumers, as well as upselling to our current clientele in close collaboration with our partners or on our own.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Using the CRM and sales management system to manage the sales process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Locating key bureaucrats on our own and establishing contacts with them either directly or in close collaboration with our partners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Managing stakeholders both inside and outside the project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborating with several bank partners Background &amp;amp; Education.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;6+ years of experience in the solution selling environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Experience in pitching to the CXOs of medium- to large scaled enterprises.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Experience in selling products that impact the bottom lines of global brands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Must have a customer centric approach with prior corporate client facing experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Fluency in local languages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Sales experience in the fin-tech sector would be preferable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The capacity to efficiently arrange, prioritise, and manage customer relationships in order to optimise activity that generates income.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;To quickly and directly seal a contract.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to promote change and make decisions with commercial heft.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;High level of motivation, self-drive, and independence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
