&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop a clear understanding of key business processes, analyze key financial metrics, provide value add analysis on core finance and controllership activities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with cross functional teams, identify and track appropriate performance measures, key performance indicators and associated drivers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Influence and drive business decisions / action with appropriate analysis and comments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Proactively reviewing financial information, identifying exceptions / inconsistencies, initiating action and follow-up for logical closure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
