&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Payroll sales Senior Manager will be a critical resource for the RazorpayX Payroll team and will be responsible for scaling up the business multifold from the current levels we are operating at.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Beginning from identifying problems, bringing ideas and solutions to the table and solving the problems through processes, people and product, this will demand working and collaborating in a highly complex environment with its own share of ambiguities and the demand for agility and driving results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This role will involve collaborating with cross-functional teams, creating and experimenting with new sales pitches and enhancing the quality of customer conversations and customer handling.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
