&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Lead, manage and drive new acquisitions for the RazorpayX Payroll.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build/Drive process efficiencies and implement controlling mechanisms for the team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build and set OKRs and KRAs for individuals and for the team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work with strategy, senior management, cross-functional teams, recruitment teams and other relevant stakeholders to forecast and manage business requirements for RazorpayX.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Track and present key business metrics and build forecasting models, understand gaps in the process, and come up with the right acquisition strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Conceptualize and run experiments and share insights and takeaways from them in a clear and presentable manner with stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Should have/build a deep level understanding of payments/fintech markets demands and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;trends.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Should have experience of driving business from a team size of 20-30 sales POC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ensure maximum conversion rates through pure outbound sales efforts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Take ownership of Learning &amp;amp; Development of the SME team - Constantly train and mentor existing and new Sales folks on sales pitch, way of working and growing their competencies and skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Be actively involved in client calls and execute negotiations as and when required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
