&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Understanding of productivity and input metrics that impact sales output&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Good at people management and strong interpersonal skills - Knowledge of the various levers of team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Strong communication and presentation skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Proven experience in a customer facing role. Should have worked with customers in managing requirements and engaging in solution selling.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A strong work ethic and a result oriented approach.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Opportunities as part of our Solutions Consultants are endless. In this role, You will be responsible for working with the enterprise sales account executives to identify customer business goals and challenges, determine customer requirements, quantify Ezetap business value, coordinate with the Sales &amp;amp; Engineering team to deliver executive level, compelling and differentiating solutions, presentations/demonstrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You will be driving the strategic viewpoint of the org towards the verticals solutions for the org and be the change leader for innovative solutions which solves a larger problem of the vertical. In this role you will be building product solutions, custom solutions, lead RFP’s for large enterprise deals and be the catalyst for revenue attainment by enabling enterprise sales teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Love the idea of being a technology &amp;amp; solutions evangelist and are excited about connecting dots and envisioning new opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
