&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Hands on technology practitioner – Get your hands dirty with APIs, technical definitions and stitching solutions between partner ecosystems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to drive customer conversation and talking about solutions and presentations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Past experience at a fintech company with exposure to banks or part of the product team of a bank will be an advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Opportunities as part of our Solutions Consultants are endless. In this role, You will be responsible for working with the enterprise sales account executives to identify customer business goals and challenges, determine customer requirements, quantify Ezetap business value, coordinate with the Sales &amp;amp; Engineering team to deliver executive level, compelling and differentiating solutions, presentations/demonstrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You will be driving the strategic viewpoint of the org towards the verticals solutions for the org and be the change leader for innovative solutions which solves a larger problem of the vertical. In this role you will be building product solutions, custom solutions, lead RFP’s for large enterprise deals and be the catalyst for revenue attainment by enabling enterprise sales teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Love the idea of being a technology &amp;amp; solutions evangelist and are excited about connecting dots and envisioning new opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Can manage multiple internal &amp;amp; external stakeholders and have productive discussions with them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Have technology consulting chops and can stitch solutions from a bouquet of features.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Loves working with banks and sales teams to translate business requirements to solutions and also, in tandem with product, engineering and customer success team to take such solutions to customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Working with the sales and customer success teams to identify customer business goals and challenges, review account opportunities and influence sales processes to leverage the best of Ezetap&#39;s product suite and solutions offerings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;To determine customer requirements, quantify Ezetap business value, coordinate with the Sales &amp;amp; Engineering team to deliver executive level, compelling and differentiating presentations/demonstrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Understanding Ezetap&#39;s product suite and roadmap and chart multiple offerings and stated needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Meeting Customer technical teams to gather business and technical pain-points and insights and arrive at solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Understanding customers business use case and pitching Ezetap product and solutions to cater their requirements and helping close deal with sales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Working with Ezetap product and engineering teams to implement proposed solutions and with customer success team for deploying the same to customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;5 to 7 years’ experience in pre-sales or technical consulting with enterprise software, preferably in a product company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Must be MBA graduate who understands technology as well.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Outstanding communication skills – Someone who does not let geographical distances create any communication gaps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Hands on technology practitioner – Get your hands dirty with APIs, technical definitions and stitching solutions between partner ecosystems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to drive customer conversation and talking about solutions and presentations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;textLayer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Past experience at a fintech company with exposure to banks or part of the product team of a bank will be an advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Technical Account Manager you will be acting as the dedicated primary point of contact for all technical and product level activities or discussions post go-live for all our Super Enterprise Merchants (accounts).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will build healthy relationships with customer’s tech contacts, help them unblock challenges, and turn them into advocates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will understand merchant queries, analyze them and do hands-on troubleshooting to ensure merchant’s day-to-day technical challenges are resolved in a timely and professional manner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will have a good understanding of the Razorpay product stack.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will report Issues or bugs to Product /Software engineering teams by raising Jira and work towards a resolution with collaboration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will Advocate and drive Merchant behaviour as well as identify new opportunities where Razorpay products and technologies can better fit the merchant’s business of monetary transactions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will work as a subject matter expert and drive all best practices with the merchant, document all tech related info, gather feedback and requested enhancements and develop detailed business requirements and represent the client in product prioritization cycles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;TAM will work very closely with Sales, Product and Engineering teams on a day to day basis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;2+ years experience in a technical product and SaaS disciplines in a customer facing role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;B.Tech/M.Tech degree in Computer Science/Information Science and Technical certifications is a plus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Previous experience in Customer success and/or account management more from a technical point of view in a SaaS environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent in written and verbal communication and good in presentation skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent multitasking and project management skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Experience in JIRA, Zendesk or similar tools.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Basic programming experience will be a plus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to uncover evolving customer requirements and map to platform features.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Exceptional project management and organizational skills - especially in coordinating meetings and follow ups with global stakeholders across multiple time zones and discipline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Technical Program Manager - Technical Projects on the team you will manage enterprise merchant &amp;amp; enterprise partnership merchant implementation projects internally &amp;amp; externally.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles &amp;amp; Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Manage internal product champion program across Sales &amp;amp; Key Accounts Teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Manage internal product to verticalisation process and Internal improvement projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Custom Implementation projects end to end.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Lead program definition, planning, and execution of assigned Program(s), which are made up of multiple projects, ensuring critical success factors are defined and monitored and the business objectives are achieved.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Program definition and scoping, owning the program plan and the deliverables required for the program’s success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop and manage an integrated program schedule, monitor and report on progress.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Liaise &amp;amp; Manage Requirements with cross-functional teams to meet Program objectives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Present Program(s) status on a regular basis to senior executives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Provide deep insights to leadership on what&#39;s going well and what is not across projects/programs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Manage product road map to impact assessment delivered of business ask.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At the heart of this role is delivery. You will be a technical problem solver on the team, identifying innovative solutions to project deadlocks and resolving issues and constraints through consensus and sound judgment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Be responsible for making project decisions, and achieving tactical goals while retaining a strategic focus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Prioritize projects, leveraging data to drive decisions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Establish excellent working relations with all internal and external partners with an emphasis on removing roadblocks to program success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;5 - 8 years of experience in a technical project/program management role, preferably in a related industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;A Bachelor’s Degree or equivalent in Engineering, or a related field.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to adapt to new technologies and learn quickly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Effectively communicate, Ability to influence and steer leadership, and senior management on Project / Program decisions, bottleneck resolution, Program progress and roadmap.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Possess in-depth technical understanding of agile software development lifecycle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Extensive experience defining programs and implementing them across a team focused on delivering outcomes that meet rapidly evolving customer needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong presentation skills with a high degree of comfort speaking with executives, technical leaders, external partners and developers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Insatiable curiosity and ability to understand architectural and technical aspects of projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;A proven ability to bring clarity to ambiguous situations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to handle multiple competing priorities in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to interact with diverse technical and non-technical groups, spanning all organisational levels.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Knowledge of project management elements, life cycles, tools, and reporting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Good to have: PMI, CSM, PSM Certifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Razorpay was founded by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/kumarshashank/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw1H2eeqfjnUDt3iT_Cg-jfh&quot;&gt; Shashank Kumar&lt;/a&gt; and&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshilmathur/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw3k1sK1wrIz5HKLsZA8-mTC&quot;&gt; Harshil Mathur&lt;/a&gt; in 2014. Razorpay is building a new-age digital banking hub (Neobank) for businesses in India with the mission is to enable frictionless banking and payments experiences for businesses of all shapes and sizes. What started as a B2B payments company is processing billions of dollars of payments for lakhs of businesses across India.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a full-stack financial services organisation, committed to helping Indian businesses with comprehensive and innovative payment and business banking solutions built over robust technology to address the entire length and breadth of the payment and banking journey for any business. Over the past year, we&#39;ve disbursed loans worth millions of dollars in loans to thousands of businesses. In parallel, Razorpay is reimagining how businesses manage money by simplifying business banking (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/x/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/x/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ab_bX0WbaTqedmVsyWBbZ&quot;&gt; Razorpay X&lt;/a&gt;) and enabling capital availability for businesses (via&lt;a href=&quot;https://razorpay.com/capital/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://razorpay.com/capital/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw2ymFZuuzdG2i4lPyqQYP5I&quot;&gt; Razorpay Capital&lt;/a&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will be part of our org leadership team and will drive multiple products and product lines with company-wide and industry-wide impact. This role leads our SME group and focuses on Mid-market, Startups &amp;amp; MSMEs and the incoming leader will get the opportunity to set &amp;amp; execute the winning strategy for us in these customer segments. Specifically, the role currently includes 3 charters - SME Growth &amp;amp; Experience, MSME Apps &amp;amp; Magic Checkout. Come on board and shape India’s digital payments future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Owner Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; As a Product Leader, you will be expected to be an intrapreneur at Razorpay who exhibits an owner mindset and is comfortable operating boundary-less. You embrace as well as excel and thrive in front of a complex, ambiguous, and uncertain challenge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Set processes and systems to scale the team. Mentor and invest in the growth of your team. Identify hiring needs and own hiring end to end in your area. Lead from the front and be comfortable being hands-on.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategy: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Craft out our long-term vision and strategy to win the customer segments you are driving. Identify new product lines and innovation opportunities. Craft the right goals &amp;amp; enable the team to build their execution roadmaps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Drive product conceptualization, product development, execution and Go-to-Market via your team. Leaders at Razorpay are expected to be comfortable in being hands-on.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enable excellence at scale: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Your role will be to derive excellence across the org and set high standards for the org to be ahead of the curve.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will be a good fit for this role if&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You think customer backward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You have a strong focus on customer experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You understand technology, but love customer-first &amp;amp; business-first thinking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You are comfortable working hands-on as a leader in a fast-paced start-up environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You are curious about metrics, execution processes, macro trends.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Problem-solving and detail orientation come naturally to you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Energetic self-starter with the hunger to work independently in a competitive and fast-paced environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3a65a3c2-7fff-88ff-9e94-8ab11a050d04&quot;&gt;Razorpay believes in and follows an equal employment opportunity policy that doesn&#39;t discriminate on gender, religion, sexual orientation, colour, nationality, age, etc. We welcome interests and applications from all groups and communities across the globe. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gmail_default&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;m_2989597180337834284gmail-m_4972969247898306296gmail-docs-internal-guid-3d0a9248-7fff-a2fd-6fa3-5026f85768d7&quot;&gt;Follow us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.linkedin.com/company/razorpay/mycompany/&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0f6sCrv8Ce3IHBvN2Sev8Z&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Razorpay&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-saferedirecturl=&quot;https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/Razorpay&amp;amp;source=gmail&amp;amp;ust=1660290870959000&amp;amp;usg=AOvVaw0ViuP9uutFg1qFCm2nHeh1&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
